Trainers Ethogram - Outcome (GD, AD, W) - Post-Hoc

Marinara Marcato

Introduction

This document shows the data analysis carried out to investigate dog’s behavioral data considering the ethograms filled out by two trainers.

Data Exploration

Columns: Variables

The ethogram comprised of the following types and number of variables.

Rows: Dogs

Total number of dogs with DC1 and DC2:

## Dogs with DC1:  75
## DC1 & Outcome: 74
## Dogs with DC2:  51
## DC2 & Outcome: 51
